summary: I’m a thinker, passionate about solving puzzles and challenging myself everyday with something new. I create tailored experiences by transforming TypeScript into functionality. My focus is on Web Technologies and integrating scalable tools into the projects I work with. Fluent in Node.JS, Angular, TypeScript, Python, with know-how on NoSQL databases such as MongoDB and DynamoDB. Amazon Web Services is my platform of choice, followed by Azure DevOps. Certified by IBM on Docker and private Blockchain Hyperledger Fabric.
